numpy


The following variables are set in the submission script
1.    PYTHONPATH must include the pyflamestk module
2.    LAMMPS_BIN must be set to the LAMMPS binary.  Since pyflamestk uses MPI 
for parallization, at the current time LAMMPS cannot.

